      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! It honestly breaks my heart a little to post this, but it\u2019s time for my pride and joy to find a new garage. I\u2019ve treated this beauty like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, never seen a salt-covered road, and pampered with the best wax. She\u2019s in stunning condition, looking just as sharp as the day I picked her up. You might find a tiny, honest mark if you really go looking, but she\u2019s a total showstopper that drives like a dream. I\u2019d love for her to go to someone who will appreciate her as much as I have. Come on over, let\u2019s talk cars, and you can see this gem in person!",
